Observed streamflow (daily)

Source: R/datasets.R
qobserved.Rd

Daily discharge at the outlet gauge of the example basin.

Usage

qobserved

Format

Tibble/data.frame with:

Date

Date (daily).

Flow

Discharge (m^3/s).

Source

National Meteorology and Hydrology Service of Peru (SENAMHI).

See also

Other Data: example_basin_datasets, gridded_climate_netcdfs, riv1, subs1, swat_txtinout_data

Examples

head(qobserved)
#> # A tibble: 6 × 2
#>   Date        Flow
#>   <date>     <dbl>
#> 1 2010-01-01  13.8
#> 2 2010-01-02  14.0
#> 3 2010-01-03  14.3
#> 4 2010-01-04  16.7
#> 5 2010-01-05  20.7
#> 6 2010-01-06  15.9
# plot(qobserved$Date, qobserved$Flow, type = "l",
#      xlab = "Date", ylab = "Flow (m^3/s)")
